// Man page for specs
manSpecs="SPECS(1)                         X Shell Manual                         SPECS(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    specs - System specifications calculator
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>specs</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Display a system specifications calculator showing hardware
    and system information for the current machine.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>specs</b>
    Show system specifications calculator
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>ifconfig</b>, <b>iwconfig</b>, <b>stats</b>"